{"tid":2089289,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國更新對港旅遊警示指被拘留風險增加","createTime":"2020-07-01T14:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T15:08:25.000Z","uid":21470,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f507d8e895f741a3406646bc4522347b3d5aa0bb","tid":2089289,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T14:52:20.000Z","msg":"英國更新對港旅遊警示指被拘留風險增加<br />\n01.07.2020 21:38<br />\n<br />\n英國更新對香港的旅遊警示，指因應港區國安法生效，在香港被拘留及驅逐出境的風險增加。英國外交部表示，大陸當局可以在某些情況下，根據港區國安法而將一些個人拘留，最高可判處終身監禁，因此對違反新法例的非永久居民來說，拘留和驅逐出境的風險增加。而由於近期的政治敏感性提高，抗議及暴力活動亦可能增加。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1326230&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1326230%26csid%3D261_367&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9QjGR3CVFSgRSSfEWrWQqBA%3D&h=9ee6004d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1326230&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"174ba580c60d8efd42164c929b1848e6a4a841dc","tid":2089289,"uid":127929,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:05:17.000Z","msg":"應該加多句提防人質外交<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe7cb5830601485ad667ca96ebab8dbad61a653","tid":2089289,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"174ba580c60d8efd42164c929b1848e6a4a841dc","tid":2089289,"uid":127929,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:05:17.000Z","msg":"應該加多句提防人質外交<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:06:17.000Z","msg":"學加拿大"},{"pid":"26556a691f31737e79efad6ce930852fb7e4b4fb","tid":2089289,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" 